---
title: One-Pan Chicken & Israeli Couscous Bowl with Parmesan Cheese
description: This dish is a delectable pot of chicken and veggies. You can often find the blend of soffritto mix and golden couscous
sitting beneath a rainbow of veggies and succulent chicken, keeping warm and smelling amazing. Tonight though, the
end of the rainbow is at your dinner table. We swear it will appear there like magic!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
